  <brief_title>Intra-articular Corticosteroid Injection Compared With Single-Shot Hyaluronic Acid for Treatment of Osteoarthritis Knee</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intra-articular Corticosteroid Injection Compared With Single-Shot Hyaluronic Acid for Treatment of Osteoarthritis Knee: A Prospective, Double-blind Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
