  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Corticosteroid and Hylan G-F 20 are both effective in improving pain and function of
      osteoarthritic knee patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Corticosteroid and Hylan G-F 20 are both effective in improving pain and function of
      osteoarthritic knee patients up to 6 months.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
